        <section id= "issue2">
            <h2>
                What to do when home page displays that unable to fetch any survey details?
            </h2>
            <h3>
                Text on screen
            </h3>
            <p>
                Unable to fetch data. Please check Internet connectivity.
            </p>
            <h3>
                Screenshot
            </h3>
            <img src="/static/image/Issue2.png" alt="Error 2" height="400" width="1200">
            <h3>
                Possible cause
            </h3>
            <p>
                The application is not able to make a request to the server.
            </p>
            <h3>
                Solution
            </h3>
            <p>
                Check internet connectivity. If the user is connected to the internet and the error persists, ask the
                user to double check whether correct url for the server has been entered. If the error persists, check
                server logs to see if the request actually came through.
            </p>
