        <section id="issue7">
            <h2>
                What to do when the loader on submit screen does not go away for a long time?
            </h2>
            <h3>
                Text on screen
            </h3>
            <h3>
                Possible cause
            </h3>
            <p>
                The call to server is not getting completed. Possible cause is that the request was made and then the
                user lost internet connection.
            </p>
            <h3>
                Solution
            </h3>
            <p>
                Quit app and try again. Ensure that the internet connectivity is there and is proper, not intermittent.
            </p>
            <br>
