        <section id="issue8">
            <h2>
                What needs to be done if a blank page is displayed after the survey is started?
            </h2>
            <h3>
                Text on screen
            </h3>
            <p>
                Start Survey takes the user to a blank page that has something like :{{question}}{{answer.answerText}}
            </p>
            <h3>
                Screenshot
            </h3>
            <img src="/static/image/Issue8.png" alt="Error 2" height="400" width="1200">
            <h3>
                Possible cause
            </h3>
            <p>
                The user has landed on the survey page but the app doesn’t have the questions. This should never happen,
                but if it happens, the cause is that the request to “get_survey” didn’t complete properly.
            </p>
            <h3>
                Solution
            </h3>
            <p>
                Quit app and try again. Ensure that the internet connectivity is there and is proper, not intermittent.
            </p>
